sentences: Aiko Kayō (嘉陽 愛子, Kayō Aiko, born December 11, 1985) is a singer, and actress.
She has released 12 singles and 2 albums on the Avex Trax label in Japan.
She has also performed with the musical units Kingyo (金魚) and A Girls.
Pretty Private, published on November 11, 2004, by Kadokawa Shoten.
